<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" data-theme="cyberpunk">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contact page</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/main.css">
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen bg-base-100">
    <%- include('partial/header' , { page: '/products'})-%>

    <div class="hero min-h-96 bg-gradient-to-r from-secondary to-accent" style="background-image: url('Asseta/prod2.jpg'); background-blend-mode: overlay;">
        <div class="hero-overlay bg-opacity-60"></div>
        <div class="hero-content text-center text-neutral-content">
          <div class="max-w-md">
            <h1 class="mb-5 text-5xl font-bold">Our Product</h1>
            <p class="mb-5">Deivering quality product that adds value to your workflow</p>
            <button class="btn btn-primary">Explore</button>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex justify-center mt-8">
        <div class="stats stats-horizontal shadow">
          <div class="stat">
            <div class="stat-title">User Globally</div>
            <div class="stat-value text-primary">50M</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <div class="stat-title">Countries</div>
            <div class="stat-value text-secondary">20+</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <div class="stat-title">Awards</div>
            <div class="stat-value text-accent">15+</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    
      <main class="container mx-auto p-6">
        <section class="py-16">
            <div class="text-center mb-12">
              <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">Our Featured Products</h2>
              <div class="badge badge-secondary badge-lg">Premium Quality</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                <!-- Brand Strategy Card -->
                <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-2xl hover:shadow-3xl transition-all duration-300">
                  <figure class="px-10 pt-10">
                    <img src="Asseta/lms.jpeg" alt="Brand Strategy" class="rounded-xl h-48 w-full object-cover"/>
                  </figure>
                  <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                      <div class="badge badge-primary">Enterprise</div>
                      <div class="badge badge-outline">Learning</div>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="card-title text-primary">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
                        </svg>
                        Learning Management System
                      </h3>
                      <p class="text-base-content/80 leading-relaxed">
                        Learning Management System (LMS) is a software application designed to manage, deliver, 
                        and track educational courses and training programs. It provides a centralized platform for content creation, 
                        student enrollment, progress monitoring, assessments, and communication, 
                        making learning more efficient and accessible for individuals and organizations
                      </p>
                      <div class="card-actions justify-end mt-4">
                        <div class="rating rating-sm">
                          <input type="radio" name="rating-1" class="mask mask-star-2 bg-orange-400" />
                          <input type="radio" name="rating-1" class="mask mask-star-2 bg-orange-400" />
                          <input type="radio" name="rating-1" class="mask mask-star-2 bg-orange-400" />
                          <input type="radio" name="rating-1" class="mask mask-star-2 bg-orange-400" />
                          <input type="radio" name="rating-1" class="mask mask-star-2 bg-orange-400" checked />
                        </div>
                        <a role="button" class="btn btn-primary" href="/lm_lms">
                          Learn More
                          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
                          </svg>
                        </a>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
        
                  <!-- Visual Identity Card -->
                  <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-2xl hover:shadow-3xl transition-all duration-300">
                    <figure class="px-10 pt-10">
                      <img src="Asseta/cm2.png" alt="Visual Identity" class="rounded-xl h-48 w-full object-cover"/>
                    </figure>
                    <div class="card-body">
                      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                        <div class="badge badge-secondary">Customer</div>
                        <div class="badge badge-outline">Enterpise</div>
                      </div>
                      <h3 class="card-title text-secondary">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
                          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z" />
                        </svg>
                        Customer Relationship Management
                      </h3>
                      <p class="text-base-content/80 leading-relaxed">
                        A Customer Relationship Management (CRM) system is a technology solution that helps businesses 
                        manage and analyze customer interactions and data throughout the customer lifecycle. 
                        Its primary purpose is to improve customer service relationships and assist in customer retention and drive sales growth by centralizing customer information, 
                        automating sales and marketing processes, and providing insights into customer behavior.
                      </p>
                      <div class="card-actions justify-end mt-4">
                        <div class="rating rating-sm">
                          <input type="radio" name="rating-2" class="mask mask-star-2 bg-orange-400" />
                          <input type="radio" name="rating-2" class="mask mask-star-2 bg-orange-400" />
                          <input type="radio" name="rating-2" class="mask mask-star-2 bg-orange-400" />
                          <input type="radio" name="rating-2" class="mask mask-star-2 bg-orange-400" />
                          <input type="radio" name="rating-2" class="mask mask-star-2 bg-orange-400" checked />
                        </div>
                        <a role="button" class="btn btn-secondary" href="/lm_lms">
                         Learn More
                          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
                          </svg>
                        </a>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
          </section>
      </main>
      <%- include('partial/footer' , { page: '/products'})-%>

</body>    
</html>